{"tid":2418946,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"皇室決裂｜哈里梅根首現身宣傳自家Podcast節目 續用公爵頭銜惹質疑","createTime":"2021-02-23T03:59:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T07:32:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2d0b8417d7df152c2cbc55260c31d42d49002a8b","tid":2418946,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T03:59:51.000Z","msg":"英國哈里王子與夫人梅根宣佈正式脫離皇室後，引發連串風波，二人周一首次露面，為即將在音樂串流平台Spotify推出的專屬Podcast（網絡廣播節目）宣傳，名為「Archewell Audio」的Podcast節目首集將於本月29日上架，而他們與Spotify簽約的金額據報多達3,000萬英鎊（約3.1億港幣）。<br />\n<br />\n在宣傳片中，哈里王子和梅根仍然使用薩塞克斯公爵及夫人頭銜，引起外界對其名銜的疑問。根據規定，二人不能再使用「殿下」（His/Her Royal Highness）的皇室頭銜，以及皇室（royal）字眼。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210223/4LNXFXLNPNEO7NNURRNWD2XXXI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210223%2F4LNXFXLNPNEO7NNURRNWD2XXXI%2F&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2Xk8L9AbO9EvXEPTzVQ1jYSs%3D&h=84bf5427\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210223%2F4LNXFXLNPNEO7NNURRNWD2XXXI%2F&h=f4483c8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210223/4LNXFXLNPNEO7NNURRNWD2XXXI/</a>"},{"pid":"14dc78d2f8edbf1e7267860c5488fefe1ee16eff","tid":2418946,"uid":77196,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T04:01:18.000Z","msg":"面皮再厚咬住唔放都冇撚用，事頭婆好緊張皇室聲譽，小心俾佢屌到你屎忽開花 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0300f26134b3fc46d6cd80be3c4a626cbb2459c4","tid":2418946,"uid":42762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T04:02:14.000Z","msg":"3.1億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b32c3e957122d8ce95d1aeccfb2d952ee940af","tid":2418946,"uid":256837,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T04:02:28.000Z","msg":"（前）皇室KOL"},{"pid":"037c065798b134343e36ae9401e64cf5538a5f0b","tid":2418946,"uid":291526,"like":3,"dislike":0,"